rows.label: qst200318_msg0001
rows.name: Oh! You're back!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0002
rows.name: How did it go? Not that I need to ask!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0003
rows.name: Well...

rows.label: qst200318_msg0004
rows.name: Hey, everyone!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0005
rows.name:
The Blade and Drivers I told
you about defeated the Gogol!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0006
rows.name: No, listen to me...

rows.label: qst200318_msg0007
rows.name: Whoa! Now we can mine in peace!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0008
rows.name:
Yes, and we no longer have to
sleep in fear of the Gogol!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0009
rows.name: Excellent, excellent! You are our hero!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0010
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Wooooooooh!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0012
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling ]Wh-what's gotten into
you all of a sudden?!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0013
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Listen to me!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0014
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling ]I did not defeat the
Gogol. I let it go.

rows.label: qst200318_msg0015
rows.name: You let it go?!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0016
rows.name: What do you mean?!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0017
rows.name:
No! Does that mean it might
attack the city again?!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0018
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Wrong!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0019
rows.name: [ML:Feeling ]They... will not do such a thing.

rows.label: qst200318_msg0020
rows.name:
The Gogols were driven from
their home by the people here.

rows.label: qst200318_msg0021
rows.name:
That is why... they attacked
to protect their family.

rows.label: qst200318_msg0022
rows.name:
Fighting... is not good. I
properly... scolded the Gogol.

rows.label: qst200318_msg0023
rows.name:
But you, who steal their
home... are also in the wrong.

rows.label: qst200318_msg0024
rows.name: I... will scold you too!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0026
rows.name: ...I am... not a hero.

rows.label: qst200318_msg0027
rows.name:
The Gogol that protects its
family... is the hero.

rows.label: qst200318_msg0028
rows.name:
You all... should be able
to understand that.

rows.label: qst200318_msg0029
rows.name:
All of you... can live
together with the Gogols.

rows.label: qst200318_msg0030
rows.name:
Please... do not steal the
Gogols' home anymore!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0031
rows.name: ...Jikarao...

rows.label: qst200318_msg0032
rows.name: ...Jikarao...

rows.label: qst200318_msg0033
rows.name: ...Jikarao...

rows.label: qst200318_msg0034
rows.name: ...Jikarao...

rows.label: qst200318_msg0035
rows.name: ...You're right!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0036
rows.name:
I'll persuade the higher-ups to
stop any more mining in that area!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0037
rows.name: Really?

rows.label: qst200318_msg0038
rows.name:
Yeah. After you put it like
that, we've gotta do something.

rows.label: qst200318_msg0039
rows.name:
Having your home destroyed is awful
for people and Gogols alike.

rows.label: qst200318_msg0040
rows.name:
There's no reason we should
do to Gogols what we wouldn't
want done to us.

rows.label: qst200318_msg0041
rows.name: You all agree, right?

rows.label: qst200318_msg0042
rows.name:
Yeah, no problem. Your feelings
reached our hearts, loud and clear.

rows.label: qst200318_msg0043
rows.name: Hey, Jikarao-san.

rows.label: qst200318_msg0044
rows.name:
You didn't just save us,
you saved the Gogols too.

rows.label: qst200318_msg0045
rows.name: You really are the hero of this city!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0046
rows.name: ...I am a hero?

rows.label: qst200318_msg0047
rows.name:
That was great, Jikarao! Your
feelings got through to everyone.

rows.label: qst200318_msg0048
rows.name:
You did it, Jikarao! Your
feelings really reached them!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0049
rows.name:
Well done, Jikarao. Your resolve
has been conveyed to them all.

rows.label: qst200318_msg0050
rows.name:
Not bad at all, Jikarao! Your
feelings got across to 'em, eh!

rows.label: qst200318_msg0051
rows.name: I was... accepted by everyone?

rows.label: qst200318_msg0052
rows.name: [ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Woooooooooooooooooh!
